            </p>

            <div class="mt-8">
                <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Testimonio")" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md shadow-sm text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 hover:from-blue-600 hover:to-indigo-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out">
                    Ver otros testimonios
                </a>
